comments: I didn't use any notes and, in hindsight, I should have done that, since it would have made my life a lot easier. That said, I noticed some patterns, but still, I couldn't really memorize all the correct spellings. I do understand that the first half of the word indicates the shape, while the second half indicates the color. I could understand what kind of shape the word is trying to convey, but for the color... I would surely need some more training.
